data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT. . . MOTIVATED SELLER! RARE OPPORTUNITY FOR INVESTORS OR NEW HOME OWNER… AIRBNB, SHORT & LONG TERM LEASES PERMITTED in Desirable Gated Indian Mountain Lakes community. NEWLY UPDATED 3,000+ Sq Ft Colonial Situated on 1+ Acres. Property Features: ~ Water-Proof Hardwood Floors throughout ~ 3-Zone Heat ~ Water Filtration System ~ Finished Basement ~ 2- Car Garage ~ Heated In-Ground Pool with Waterfall & Hot Tub ~ Patio with Pergola ~ Large Deck ~   First Floor Includes: Living Room with Gas Fireplace, Dining Room, Half-Bath, Washer/Dryer area, Updated Eat-In Kitchen with all New SS Appliances, Quartz Countertops, Water-Proof Hardwood Flooring, Recessed Lighting, and Sliding Doors leading to the Deck and Pool area.   Second Floor Includes: Master Suite with an additional Sitting Room with Cathedral Ceilings and Full Bath with Double-Vanity and Sunken Tub. Additionally, 2 Bedrooms with Large Closets and Ceiling Fan. Full Bathroom with Ceramic Tile Flooring.  Fully-Finished Basement Includes: New Porcelain Flooring throughout, High Ceilings, 2 Full-Sized Bonus Rooms perfect for additional Bedrooms, Entertainment Areas and Utility Room. Close to Pocono Shops, Attractions & Restaurants. Minutes to I-80, Rts 534 & 715… Investor’s & Commuter’s Dream!
